      "text": "Built reusable React component library adopted across 5 teams, reducing development time by 40%"
    },
    {
      "bulletPointId": "bullet-id-2",
      "text": "Improved web vitals scores by 50% through code splitting and lazy loading optimization"
    },
    {
      "bulletPointId": "bullet-id-3",
      "text": "Implemented responsive design system achieving 100% accessibility compliance (WCAG 2.1 AA)"
    }
  ]
}
