## Error Responses

### 400 Bad Request - Invalid Section Order
```http
PATCH /api/v1/resume/01ARZ3NDEKTSV4RRFFQ69G5FAV/reorder HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:5000
Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order": "WorkExperience,InvalidSection,Skills"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "error": "Invalid section names: InvalidSection. Valid sections: WorkExperience, Education, Skills, Projects, Certifications, Links"
}
```

### 401 Unauthorized - Missing Token
```http
GET /api/v1/resume/01ARZ3NDEKTSV4RRFFQ69G5FAV HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:5000
```

**Response:**
```
HTTP/1.1 401 Unauthorized
```

### 404 Not Found - Resume Doesn't Exist
```http
GET /api/v1/resume/nonexistent-id HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:5000
Authorization: Bearer {token}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "error": "Resume not found"
}
```

